cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper focuses on compressing and accelerating CNN models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a new method for filter level pruning, which involves optimization and statistical analysis, indicating a potential fit for artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its method on image classification tasks, suggesting a possible fit for multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
